Third Department,

September, 1974

(September 4, 1974) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Gregory Richard Smoot, Petitioner, v. Jack R. Nevil, as Sheriff of Otsego County, Respondent.

Application for writ of habeas corpus pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd. [b], par. 2) denied. (See CPLR 7003, subd. [b].) Herlihy, P. J., Greenblott, Cooke, Sweeney and Main, JJ., concur.
